  <summary date="2021-06-10T13:32:51Z" status="Introduced in House">No Honor for Treason Act

This bill prohibits the provision of military honors at the funeral or burial of any person who has been convicted of a felony committed on January 6, 2021, in or on the U.S. Capitol buildings and grounds.</summary>
